# ============================================================================
# Account 1: Gmail Personal
# ============================================================================
IMAPAccount gmail-personal
Host imap.gmail.com
User jokinenmarko1@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show email/mail-personal/app-password"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-personal-remote
Account gmail-personal

MaildirStore gmail-personal-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail-personal/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail-personal/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail-personal
Far :gmail-personal-remote:
Near :gmail-personal-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Trash" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

